{"prompt": "Generate a website for a local artist portfolio. The website should be clean and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Local Artist Portfolio</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f4f4;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #c62828;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #e57373;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        #about, #portfolio, #contact {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        #about h2, #portfolio h2, #contact h2 {\n            color: #c62828;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n        .artist-intro, .gallery, .contact-info {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .artist-intro p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n        }\n        .gallery {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n        .gallery-item img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 250px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border: 3px solid #c62828;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .gallery-item img:hover {\n            transform: scale(1.03);\n            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .contact-info p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n        .contact-info a {\n            color: #c62828;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        .contact-info a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #c62828;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>[Artist Name]</h1>\n        <nav>\n            <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n            <a href=\"#portfolio\">Portfolio</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Me</h2>\n            <div class=\"artist-intro\">\n                <p>\n                    Welcome to my online portfolio. I am a local artist specializing in [mention your art style, e.g., abstract paintings, digital illustrations, ceramic sculptures]. My work explores themes of [mention themes] and is inspired by [mention inspirations]. I strive to create pieces that evoke emotion and spark conversation.\n                </p>\n                <p>\n                    With a passion for [mention your passion] and years of experience, I aim to bring a unique perspective to the art world. Explore my gallery to see my creations.\n                </p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"portfolio\">\n            <h2>Portfolio</h2>\n            <div class=\"gallery\">\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/c62828/ffffff?text=Artwork+1\" alt=\"Artwork 1\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/c62828/ffffff?text=Artwork+2\" alt=\"Artwork 2\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/c62828/ffffff?text=Artwork+3\" alt=\"Artwork 3\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/c62828/ffffff?text=Artwork+4\" alt=\"Artwork 4\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/c62828/ffffff?text=Artwork+5\" alt=\"Artwork 5\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/c62828/ffffff?text=Artwork+6\" alt=\"Artwork 6\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Contact Me</h2>\n            <div class=\"contact-info\">\n                <p>Interested in a commission or have a question?</p>\n                <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:your.email@example.com\">your.email@example.com</a></p>\n                <p>Follow me on: <a href=\"#\">[Social Media Link]</a></p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 [Artist Name]. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Optional: Add some subtle animations or smooth scrolling if desired\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}